{"type": "article", "id": 29908, "title": "橄榄油包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-20T23:04:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 25, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160720234539PDX7R9xGdbEf3UcV.jpeg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>饮料、酒水、甚至护肤品当中你都能见到金箔的影子，现在你在橄榄油中也能看到它们斑驳的踪迹了。瑞典品牌 <a href=\"http://myst.gr/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Myst</a> 为旗下橄榄油设计的包装或许会让人误以为是为酒水量身定制的，黑金和白银的配色分别对应加有金箔和普通的橄榄油，传递出低调奢华的感觉。这种不做额外修饰的设计风格也帮助强调了橄榄油天然纯粹的品质。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160720234559g6Nv7xaT4PefEZms.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160720234559sJcTnbRaWz5Zo8pV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160720234559Kn2XhyRow5tLSVsM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160720234559aLn4u2SWpGhx80Xe.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}